# Iran Mentor Platform 🇮🇷

A mentoring platform designed to support Iranian users with career guidance and professional development.

## 🎯 Project Goal

To connect Iranian users with experienced mentors who can help with:

- CV Review
- Resume Translation
- LinkedIn Setup
- Career & Business Advice
- Career Path Consultation

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- WordPress (Planned Backend)

## 🚀 Project Status

Currently building the front-end interface using modern responsive design.

Future plans include:

- Mentor dashboard
- Booking system
- WordPress backend integration

